bug.short_desc: First lines of qx.ui.table.Table get garbled if a qx.ui.menu.Menu context menu is opened over the first ~20 lines

long_desc.thetext:
Opening a context menu (built with qx.ui.menu.Menu) over a qx.ui.table.Table distorts the drawing of the cells under the context menu in the first ~20 lines of the table. After this the capturing of the click events and key move events seem to be desturbed.
I have built a text runnable from framework/application/sample/sourc/html/test which should show the problem.
Unfortunately the problem is not allways reproducable so you maybe need more then one attempt (by hitting CTRL+F5) to reproduce the problem.
I have also attached a screen snapshot showing the garbled lines.
